{"tid":1250001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家記住琴日個pattern","createTime":"2019-06-22T02:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T03:46:00.000Z","uid":114483,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"45fa184c3c86679be0946346ceb2cfb680a8454f","tid":1250001,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:00:32.000Z","msg":"好老實，我地琴晚係贏左，仲重要過6月任何一次發夢，因為我地已經搵到一個更重要既pattern 去對抗冷處理，詳細係點，我就唔講啦，廢事比警犬mon post，琴日有到場有周圍遊擊既人都應該記得我地點聚集人力去遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得以後lihkg 可以用作一個大方針，則係好似一開始既聚集點，到時落到場先再商議，和理非有和理非做，勇武就周圍遊擊，今次證明少人都有少人打，當然人數都好重要，但係今鋪真係做到be water，一於癱瘓個政府，警察出手就會愈搞愈大，唔出手我地就周圍不合作，再加上政府個戰術根本唔識防範於未然，幾次不合作都見唔到警犬，機會黎啦咁多位"},{"pid":"16a629e9793cefc8c247a1501e22cad0f7f07d15","tid":1250001,"uid":114483,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"有樣野好重要，醫院消防法院呢啲地方真係唔使幫收工，唔好比人分化，簡地點個陣諗啲癱瘓到又吸到民意（收工人士）既地方"},{"pid":"6d9cc6a7de7ddb0845ed2cf8c423fa9fc66373f5","tid":1250001,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121ef12c30a3d550f6ce335a3620fcdeae8c433c","tid":1250001,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f96c275034545f336bf7e227656e2c3c1c511059","tid":1250001,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c761c44decdd2a112804a24b236ae5d1ceba48b5","tid":1250001,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"警察變咗終極目標，反而真普選無人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27805b126c7112e02be82a15310edd2ae18b64c9","tid":1250001,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike"